{
  "stem": "14552.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they would-- if somebody dared to say whatever, they were either beaten up, or like this woman, she had her blood drained and she was thrown off bed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one time I said, I can't take this anymore and I-- let them kill me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then my sister and our friend gave me one yank on my arm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I almost lost this arm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They yanked me, get away, get in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the selections.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- don't you dare do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your sister needs you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't you behave like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I realized that I'm doing it not for myself, I'm hurting my sister more.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we were-- we were supportive of each other as much as we could, but standing twice a day, cold morning, hot afternoon for them to count us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were five in a row.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was called zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after they have counted and we tallied out correctly, and it didn't work the first time, they would hand us a bread which was cut into five slices.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we would-- everybody would take one slice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I invariably fainted, because I had low blood sugar when I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was weak, and I would just faint away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I managed to faint after or before, because if I would have fainted while they were counting, I would not be here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they held me from both sides, and they rubbed my neck, and they tried to keep me going.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then in the afternoon, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this went on every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got no number, because we were destined for destruction.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
